%{help=server module}%{+n}
###  %bdns module%b
   This module provides support for asynchronous DNS queries.
   This guards the bot from blocking several seconds while
   resolving IP addresses or hostnames.

   Config file variables for configuring the server module:
     %bdns-retrydelay%b    %bdns-maxsends%b    %bdns-servers%b
     %bdns-negcache%b      %bdns-cache%b

   (Use %b'.help set <variable>'%b for more info)
